d must pocket them before your opponent.\nFreestyle: Flexibility is key. Pocket any coin and rack up those points against your competition.\n\ud83d\udd33 Single Player:\nTest your skills against our AI opponents. Whether you're playing solo, partnering with an AI, or challenging multiple AIs, there's a level for everyone.\n\n\ud83d\udd33 Multiplayer Magic:\nExperience multiplayer like never before. Play one-on-one, team up with a friend against two AIs, or embrace the challenge of player + AI versus player + AI matches.\n\n\ud83d\udd33 Immersive Features:\n\nVoice Chat: Communicate with your opponents in real-time.\nOculus Avatars: Customize and flaunt your unique avatar.\nLip-Sync: Experience enhanced realism with lip-sync features.\nRediscover the joy of Carrom, whether you're a seasoned player or a newcomer. With intuitive controls, lifelike interactions, and multiple game modes, 'Real Carrom' promises endless fun and challenges. Ready to strike?\"", "short_description": "Experience authentic Carrom with a digital twist! Dive into single or multiplayer modes, challenge AI, or team up with friends, all while enjoying voice chat, Oculus avatars, and lip-sync. Choose from 'Black and White' or 'Freestyle' modes and showcase your Carrom mastery."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.visionxr.co.in/realcarromprivacypolicy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "VisionXR", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.visionxr.co.in/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1676485315806614"}, {"id": "275629210202852"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_a